{"tid":2018094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【警世】唔好再跟日程表","createTime":"2020-05-15T11:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T17:58:17.000Z","uid":7186,"like":346,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"0972002480f21d753857c9a528409373621c2313","tid":2018094,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:57:20.000Z","msg":"革命從來都唔係追求人多畫面靚，<br />\n唔係要有畫面有新聞先係抗爭緊。<br />\n如果冇上街冇畫面冇新聞，<br />\n國際會唔會當你放棄追求民主？手足係咪就等於離場？<br />\n<br />\n可能大家唔知，雨傘嘅時候就已經有獅鳥，<br />\n而今次運動亦一直有快閃裝修，只不過新聞冇報導，<br />\n原因係咩，自己諗。<br />\n<br />\n依啲冇畫面冇報導嘅新聞有威脅啲，<br />\n定係日程表多人出嚟畫面靚嘅活動有威脅啲？<br />\n我唔會話手足係送頭，每個被捕我都心痛到喊，<br />\n但日程表活動嘅成本效益已經跌到負數。<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，跟日程表出去和你SING想達到咩目的？<br />\n經濟攬炒？<br />\n如果大家有留多一陣都會見到啲店係會開返閘做生意，<br />\n唔再係以前咁關大半日。<br />\n國際關注？<br />\n外國唔知香港有警暴？<br />\n啲子彈核彈新聞早就多到摧毀宇宙，<br />\n殺人犯係唔需要再殺人嚟證明自己有罪。<br />\n<br />\n依啲效益值唔值得每次出嚟都有人被捕？<br />\n<br />\n日程表行動通晒天，便衣多過手足，<br />\n依個已經唔係和理非定勇武嘅差別。<br />\n班狗比以前更加冇人性，<br />\n你敢唔敢想像依家入去48個鐘有咩待遇？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係政治鬥爭入面低估對手係好致命嘅失誤。</span></span><br />\n喜茶單嘢已經再次證實，班狗唔係弱智。<br />\n<br />\n一捉，手足就被判幾年，<br />\n法治係死咗，但監都係要坐。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔係吹散水風叫大家乜都唔好做，<br />\n但不論和理非定勇武，<br />\n唔好再話比對家知你要做乜。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我熱愛和平，<br />\n吾支持港獨勢力係度搞爛香港，<br />\n唔想再見到你班暴徒嘅日程表。<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d70a9eed97f0047cfdab4d5c439ffd5376dc04ad","tid":2018094,"uid":7186,"like":41,"dislike":9,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:59:22.000Z","msg":"冇日程表點聚人啊？<br />\n點解需要聚人？<br />\nBe Water，快閃。"},{"pid":"2046cb14f839ee38d60931e146d9d9a80f73f29a","tid":2018094,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:00:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9be533d81f42b413802810b59f37865d258b772","tid":2018094,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:00:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc2873a9af3f99891f90d4924f34cfe8edbcbf0f","tid":2018094,"uid":278990,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"出奇不意，自己三五個朋友組隊「踢波咋」"},{"pid":"f96caae981780173f0da8b8b05e71ae8af813afe","tid":2018094,"uid":59976,"like":3,"dislike":20,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"全力專注35+，唔好再出去送頭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf99e685c1fc4688e02b8c58e93bad491f8f648","tid":2018094,"uid":7186,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"革命從來都唔係要人多畫面靚。"},{"pid":"0e19e36f7c38ad817f12de85619020430ebe0dff","tid":2018094,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:01:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0faa537bfa3bdd9a15b7d4d582716fae9ae77dd5","tid":2018094,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a595394cd5beacb600c0edc4e4940a0a20e40351","tid":2018094,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73186b21f68ab00bf10b745525051a77d7a5b387","tid":2018094,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3b6a66a8545eeadacd08f07ce4c3775a8b38209","tid":2018094,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246524ff0c648b1eef9f7200c3b9e2bbf45fe217","tid":2018094,"uid":173326,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:05:03.000Z","msg":"希望至少被咬過嘅人會明"},{"pid":"91d0c4e87c2def22b4ca45a83456b42806af8130","tid":2018094,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157d2ab114b3599cf722e224898c9d7c503eca2a","tid"